  "prompt": "What is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Treutlen County GA?",
  "response": "When looking for a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Treutlen County, GA, you may consider the following options:\n\n1. **Recovery Center of Atlanta**\n   - Location: Atlanta, GA\n   - Services: Offers a variety of treatment programs, including inpatient detox, residential treatment, and outpatient services.\n\n2. **The Dawn at The Meadows**\n   - Location: Wickenburg, AZ (this is a bit farther, but highly regarded)\n   - Services: Provides comprehensive treatments for substance abuse and offers a serene environment.\n\n3. **Hazel Street Recovery**\n   - Location: Dublin, GA (approximately 30 miles from Treutlen County)\n   - Services: Offers personalized inpatient programs and is focused on recovery and rehabilitation.\n\n4. **Betty Ford Center**\n   - Location: Offers locations in multiple states, including a facility in Georgia.\n   - Services: Known for high-quality treatment, including medical care and psychological support.\n\n5. **Peachtree Recovery Solutions**\n   - Location: Various locations in Georgia\n   - Services: Focuses on individualized treatment plans for addiction recovery.\n\nIt's important to reach out to these centers directly to understand their services, treatment options, and insurance compatibility. Additionally, consider personal needs and preferences when choosing a facility.",
